-------------------------10909 sample_num
```sql
SELECT 
    (AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) - AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'LAM' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END)) AS SME_LAM,
    (AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'LAM' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) - AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END)) AS LAM_KAM,
    (AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) - AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END)) AS KAM_SME
FROM 
    (SELECT 
        c.CustomerID, 
        y.Date, 
        SUM(y.Consumption) AS Consumption
    FROM 
        customers c 
    JOIN 
        yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID 
    WHERE 
        y.Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312'
    GROUP BY 
        c.CustomerID, 
        y.Date
    ORDER BY 
        Consumption
    LIMIT 1) AS lowest_consumption_per_segment
WHERE 
    Segment IN ('SME', 'LAM', 'KAM');
```
-------------------------10910 sample_num
```sql
SELECT 
    Segment, 
    ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN Date BETWEEN '201201' AND '201212' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) - 
            SUM(CASE WHEN Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END)) / 
           SUM(CASE WHEN Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) * 100, 2) AS Percentage_Increase
FROM 
    yearmonth
WHERE 
    Currency = 'EUR'
GROUP BY 
    Segment
ORDER BY 
    Percentage_Increase DESC;
```

-------------------------10913 sample_num

```sql
SELECT 
    SUM(y Consumption) - SUM(y Consumption) AS Difference
FROM 
    yearmonth y
WHERE 
    y.CustomerID = 7 AND y.Date LIKE '201304%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 
    SUM(y Consumption) AS Consumption
FROM 
    yearmonth y
WHERE 
    y.CustomerID = 5 AND y.Date LIKE '201304%';
```
-------------------------10914 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM (
  SELECT COUNT(*) 
  FROM transactions_1k 
  WHERE CustomerID IN (
    SELECT CustomerID 
    FROM customers 
    WHERE Segment = 'SME' 
    AND Currency = 'CZK'
  ) 
  UNION ALL 
  SELECT COUNT(*) 
  FROM transactions_1k 
  WHERE CustomerID IN (
    SELECT CustomerID 
    FROM customers 
    WHERE Segment = 'SME' 
    AND Currency = 'EUR'
  )
) AS subquery 
WHERE subquery.COUNT(*) > (
  SELECT COUNT(*) 
  FROM transactions_1k 
  WHERE CustomerID IN (
    SELECT CustomerID 
    FROM customers 
    WHERE Segment = 'SME' 
    AND Currency = 'EUR'
  )
) - (
  SELECT COUNT(*) 
  FROM transactions_1k 
  WHERE CustomerID IN (
    SELECT CustomerID 
    FROM customers 
    WHERE Segment = 'SME' 
    AND Currency = 'CZK'
  )
);
```

-------------------------10919 sample_num
```sql
SELECT 
    g.Country, 
    COUNT(*) AS Total_VFM_Gas_Stations
FROM 
    gasstations g
JOIN 
    transactions_1k t ON g.GasStationID = t.GasStationID
JOIN 
    yearmonth y ON g.GasStationID = y.CustomerID
WHERE 
    y.Consumption > (SELECT AVG(Consumption) FROM yearmonth)
GROUP BY 
    g.Country
ORDER BY 
    Total_VFM_Gas_Stations DESC;
```

```
FROM gasstations g
JOIN transactions_1k t ON g.GasStationID = t.GasStationID
JOIN customers c ON t.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
WHERE c.Currency = 'Euro';
```

```sql
JOIN products p ON t.ProductID = p.ProductID
WHERE t.Currency = 'EUR';
```

-------------------------10935 sample_num
```
SELECT 
    TIME(transaction.Time) AS TimeOfTransaction
FROM 
    transactions_1k
WHERE 
    transactions_1k.GasStationID IN (
        SELECT 
            gasstations.GasStationID
        FROM 
            gasstations
        WHERE 
            gasstations.ChainID = 11
    )
ORDER BY 
    TimeOfTransaction;
```

-------------------------10948 sample_num
```sql
SELECT 
  ym.Date, 
  SUM(t.Amount) AS Total_Spend
FROM 
  transactions_1k t
  JOIN yearmonth ym ON t.CustomerID = ym.CustomerID AND ym.Date LIKE '2012-01-%'
WHERE 
  t.Amount = 124.05 AND t.Date = '2012-08-24'
GROUP BY 
  ym.Date
```

-------------------------10953 sample_num
```sql
SELECT 
    ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT c.CustomerID) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM customers) * 100, 2) 
FROM 
    customers c 
WHERE 
    c.Currency = 'EUR' 
    AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM yearmonth ym WHERE ym.CustomerID = c.CustomerID AND ym.Date = '2012-08-25');
```
-------------------------10954 sample_num
```sql
SELECT (c2012 - c2013) / c2012 AS ConsumptionDecreaseRate
FROM (
  SELECT 
    CustomerID, 
    SUM(Consumption) AS c2012
  FROM yearmonth
  WHERE Date <= '2012-08-24'
  GROUP BY CustomerID
) AS ym2012
JOIN (
  SELECT 
    CustomerID, 
    SUM(Consumption) AS c2013
  FROM yearmonth
  WHERE Date > '2012-08-24'
  GROUP BY CustomerID
) AS ym2013
ON ym2012.CustomerID = ym2013.CustomerID
WHERE ym2012.CustomerID IN (
  SELECT CustomerID
  FROM transactions_1k
  WHERE Amount = 634.8
)
```
-------------------------10955 sample_num
```sql
SELECT gs.GasStationID, SUM(t.Amount) as TotalRevenue
FROM transactions_1k t
JOIN gasstations gs ON t.GasStationID = gs.GasStationID
GROUP BY gs.GasStationID
ORDER BY TotalRevenue DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

```sql
FROM 
    customers c
WHERE 
    c.Segment = 'Premium' AND c.Country = 'SVK'
```

-------------------------10958 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.Description AS FullProductName, SUM(t.Amount) AS TotalSales
FROM transactions_1k t
JOIN products p ON t.ProductID = p.ProductID
GROUP BY p.Description
ORDER BY TotalSales DESC
LIMIT 5;
```
-------------------------10959 sample_num
```sql
SELECT 
    c.CustomerID, 
    c.Currency, 
    AVG(t.Price / t.Amount) AS avg_price_per_item
FROM 
    transactions_1k t
JOIN 
    customers c ON t.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
GROUP BY 
    c.CustomerID, 
    c.Currency
ORDER BY 
    SUM(t.Amount) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------10960 sample_num
```sql
SELECT g.Country
FROM gasstations g
JOIN transactions_1k t ON g.GasStationID = t.GasStationID
WHERE t.ProductID = 2
GROUP BY g.Country
ORDER BY SUM(t.Price) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------10961 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.CustomerID, y.Date, y.Consumption
FROM customers c
JOIN yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
WHERE y.Date LIKE '201208%'
AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM transactions_1k t
  WHERE t.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
  AND t.ProductID = 5
  AND t.Price / t.Amount > 29.00
)
```
